SummaryEnglish: Suzu, a first-year junior high school student in Iwaki's hot spring town, and her classmate Fumi formed a hula club on a whim. With the addition of Mona, a transfer student from Finland, he gathered friends and spent his youth on hula dancing in order to participate in the contest, but... Due to the influence of the new coronavirus, club activities are voluntarily restrained, what will happen to the hula club! ?
